com.gracenote.gnsdk
Class GnMusicIdMatch

java.lang.Object
  com.gracenote.gnsdk.GnMusicIdMatch

public class GnMusicIdMatch
extends java.lang.Object

MusicID Match uses a combination of waveform fingerprinting technologies to match tracks within an end-user's collection to tracks within a cloud music provider's catalog, enabling instant playback from all devices without requiring upload.

The GnMusicId and GnMusicIdFile classes provide methods for generating fingerprints from audio files and streaming music.

public static java.lang.String version()
Retrieves the MusicID Match SDK's version string.

Remarks:

This API can be called at any time, after successfully getting a GnManager instance. The returned string is a constant. Do not attempt to modify or delete.

Example version string: 1.2.3.123 (Major.Minor.Improvement.Build)

Major: New functionality

Minor: New or changed features

Improvement: Improvements and fixes

Build: Internal build number
